Paramedics from ER24 arrived on the scene at approximately 11.30am to find one of the vehicles lying on its side in the middle of the road. Sadly the driver of the overturned vehicle was found with fatal injuries inside the vehicle. He was later declared dead on the scene said ER24 spokesman Werner Vermaak. The passenger along with the two occupants of the other vehicle was found on the scene with moderate injuries. They were assessed and later transported to Carletonville Hospital he added.